import React, { Component } from 'react'
import WrapComponent from '@/components/wrapper'
import Tables from './campaignList'
import { campaignListData } from './dummyData'

const headers = [
    { key: 'name', value: 'Campaign Name' },
    { key: 'campaignType', value: 'Type' },
    { key: 'channel', value: 'Channel' },
    { key: '', value: 'Actions' },
    { key: 'scheduleTime', value: 'Schedule Time' },
    { key: '', value: '' },
    { key: '', value: '' },
]

class CampaignManage extends Component {
    render() {
        return (
            <>
                <WrapComponent>
                    <Tables loading={false} data={campaignListData.campaigns} headers={headers} />
                </WrapComponent>
            </>
        )
    }
}

export default CampaignManage
